## Limiting Cases Checked
| Limit | Expected | Obtained | Status |
|-------|----------|----------|--------|

## Assumptions and Their Validity
1. [Assumption — valid when — breaks when — impact if violated]

## Suggestions
1. [Additional checks or alternative derivations to consider]
```
